Inkampani ephaka ugesi kuleli, i-Eskom namhlanje imemezele ukuthi kusukela ngehora lesine ntambama kuzophinde kube  nokuhamba kukagesi kuze kube yihora leshumi. kusihlwa Bathi lokhu kwenziwe yizinkinga ababhekane nazo njengoba kukhona isizinda esiphaka ugesi esithwele kanzima. Esitatimendeni u-Eskom uthe ama-generator ayisithupha eMedupi, Tutuka, Kendal, Majuba naseGrootvlei kuye kwadingeka abuyiselwe emuva ukuyolungiswa. U-Eskom uveze ukuthi badinga ama-megawatts awu-2 000 ukuze izinto zihambe kahle. 